===Etymology 2===
Cognate with {{term|雨|ame|rain}}. Found in compounds. The /s/ either represents [[w:epenthesis|epenthesis]] between two vowels in compounds or, more likely, is a reflex of an older form of the word {{term|雨|ame|rain}} only maintained in fossilized compounds. See Derived terms.

